places/ChIJ6ddYmGQZ2jER9G6abHZE-40/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURWZzhLRlB3EAE
text:
{'text': "As a student pursuing a course in mechanical and electrical engineering at BMC International College, I had a stellar experience. The faculty and staff were extremely supportive and dedicated to ensuring that I had a positive learning experience. I would like to extend my special thanks to Ma'am Ann, who went above and beyond to help me navigate through the challenging coursework and provided invaluable guidance throughout my time at the college. Her expertise and dedication truly made a difference in my academic journey.

The college provided me with a comprehensive understanding of both mechanical and electrical engineering principles, and the practical hands-on experience I gained has proven to be invaluable. The curriculum was well-structured and current, and the professors were passionate and knowledgeable in their respective fields.

The college also provided ample resources for research and practical application of the knowledge gained, and the state-of-the-art facilities and labs further enhanced my learning experience.

Overall, my time at BMC International College has been rewarding and has equipped me with the knowledge and skills necessary to excel in my future career. I am grateful for the education and support I received and would highly recommend this college to anyone seeking a quality education in the field of mechanical and electrical engineering. Thank you, BMC International College, for an exceptional learning experience.", 'languageCode': 'en'}

text:
{'text': 'BMC college is so professional in handling students matter from their applications, during their studies and till attaining of their certifications.
Vastly different from other colleges thus with professional lecturers during online class sessions during and post pandemic.

BMC staffs had done a great jobs!

I personally thanks BMC for their service and on behalf of their international students.

Looking for forward to higher degrees for upcoming students', 'languageCode': 'en'}
